thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Greg Schwartz

author: Greg Schwartz
title: Greg Schwartz
text: Hi,I just wanted to thank everyone evolved in the shipping of my package from Melbourne Australia to Merton Wisconsin USA.It came way faster than I expected it to and came with absolutely no damage what so ever.I bought this item on eBay from a seller who did not send or even list the item in the U.S.So I found it and arranged it myself online and it was super easy to book.I could not be any happier.Thank you for your great service.
